keep U.S.-style compensation practices from spreading with them.
(Compare the salary of Daimler CEO Jurgen Schrempp to that of
Chrysler CEO Bob Eaton: Schrempp earns 1/35th as much.) By James
Surowiecki. Slate. 700 words.
