<HEADER>
A6933 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MARS-CONVENTION-BOS &LR;      08-17 0769
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MARS-CONVENTION-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
GROUP HAS OTHERWORLDLY GOAL: TO SEND HUMANS TO MARS 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By DAVID L. CHANDLER  
 c.1998 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   BOULDER, Colo. _ The 750 people assembled here this week for the
