<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19980817.0153 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-17 12:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7309 &Cx1f; tab-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MONICA-AND-OJ-PRODUCT     08-17 0516
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MONICA-AND-OJ-PRODUCT-PITCHERS-AND-MORE-NYTSF </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   FROM MONICA TO O.J., CELEBRITY ENDORSERS CAN BE RISKY BUSINESS
</P>
<P>
