   &UR; SCIENCE &LR;  (``a'' code)
</P>
<P>
   BALLOON-FOSSETT (Undated) _ Balloonist Steve Fossett broke a
ballooning record, but still failed to make it around the world. He
plunged into the ocean some 500 miles off the coast of Australia.
By Malcolm W. Browne. (700 words)
