   UPCOMING:
</P>
<P>
   TENNIS:
</P>
<P>
   Men's: MFS Championships and The Hamlet Cup, August 24-30.
</P>
<P>
   Women's: U.S Hardcourt Championship, August 24-30.
</P>
<P>
   GOLF:
</P>
<P>
   PGA: Sprint International, August 20-23.
</P>
<P>
   LPGA: Minnesota LPGA Classic, August 20-23.
</P>
