   If you have questions or need a resend, please call CoxNet, the
Cox News Service, at 404-526-5456.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-WILDCARD _ ATLANTA _ Those baseball purists, who once
decried the institution of the wildcard, might be coming around a
bit now, when you consider what's taking place in the National
League. The Giants come to town Tuesday in the midst of a heated
race for a playoff position. Without the wildcard, the NL races
would be over. (Rosenberg, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m.
ET.
