<DOCNO> NYT19980817.0319 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-17 18:41 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8025 &Cx1f; tad-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-JAMAICA-VIAGRA-COX     08-17 0475
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-JAMAICA-VIAGRA-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Viagra expected to get blame in rape
 &HT;    (EDS: Moving in (i) International and (f) Financial categories.)
 &HT;    By Shelley Emling
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   MONTEGO BAY, Jamaica _ A 70-year-old businessman charged with
raping a young employee goes before a judge here today, and
