   &QL; 
BBA-ANGELS (Anaheim, Calif.) _ The Angels, in first place by a half
game over the Texas Rangers in the AL West, host the Chicago White
Sox. 7:05 p.m. &QL; 
By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.)
