   Corinthians have emerged as Brazil's top team and their coach,
 &UR; Wanderley Luxem- &LR; H  &UR; burgo &LR; , &UR;  &LR; has justifiably been named to succeed
 &UR; Mario Zagallo  &LR; as national team coach.
</P>
<P>
   Luxemburgo will also have to bring in new talent. He is expected
to add Corinthians'  &UR; Fe- &LR; H  &UR; lipe &LR; , &UR;  &LR; 21, who is considered at least
